Package gobblin.async

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AsyncRequestBuilder<D,RQ>
    An interface to build an async request from a buffer of records
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AsyncDataDispatcher<D>
    Base class with skeleton logic to dispatch a record asynchronously.
    AsyncRequest<D,RQ>
    A type of write request which may batch several records at a time.
    AsyncRequest.Thunk
    A helper class which wraps the callback It may contain more information related to each individual record
    BufferedRecord<D>
    This class represents a record in a buffer
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DispatchException
    Exception for dispatching failures.
